        <p><lb n="1"/>Oṁ svasti mānagr̥hāt sakala-satvānugrahāhita-mano-nirabhimāna-ra<lb break="no" n="2"/>maṇīya-carita-licchavi-kula-ketu-bhaṭṭāraka-mahārāja-śrī-dhruva<lb break="no" n="3"/>deva-purassaraḥ
</p>
        <lg met="vaṁśamālā" n="1">
          <l n="a">prajā-hitodyukta-viśuddha-mānasaḥ</l>
          <l n="b">prabhāva-<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->śaurya</supplied>pra <lb break="no" n="4"/>naṭāri-maṇḍalaḥ</l>
          <l n="c">guṇair upeto <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>nupamair ihātmavān</l>
          <l n="d">pr <seg met="-+-++">
              <gap quantity="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
            </seg> <lb break="no" n="5"/>m api candramā Iva</l>
        </lg>
        <!-- 
v1. Gnoli says: Metre: upajāti of vaṁśasthavila and indravaṁśā;
I wonder why: phps because the lost first syllable of pāda d;
that is why I give "vaṁśamālā" 
-->
        <p>so <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>yam ittham-bhūtaḥ kailāsa-kuṭa-bhavanād bhagava<!-- 
L5. kuṭa sic in ed. 
--><lb break="no" n="6"/>t paśupati-bhaṭṭāraka-pādānugr̥hīto bappa-pādānudhyātaḥ śrī-jiṣṇu<lb break="no" n="7"/>guptaḥ kuśalī nuppunna-draṅga-nivāsinaḥ pradhāna-purassarān kuṭumbinaḥ
<lb n="8"/>kuśalāgresaraṁ samājñāpayati viditam astu vo bhaṭṭāraka-mahārā<lb break="no" n="9"/>ja-śrī-vasurāja-śrī-mahīdeva-śrī-mānadeva-śrī-gaṇadevāsmat-pitāma<lb break="no" n="10"/>ha-śrī-bhūmagupta Ity etaiḥ pūrva-rājabhir asmad-gurubhiḥ parānugraha-pra<lb break="no" n="11"/>vr̥ttitayā śilā-paṭṭaka-śā<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->sana-dvi</supplied>tayena vo yaḥ prasāda-viśe<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->ṣai</supplied><!-- 
L11. [°tri]tayena? 
--><lb break="no" n="12"/>r anugrahaḥ kr̥to <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>bhūd vā <gap precision="low" quantity="5" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> nida-dvādaśa-bhāga-vastu-toyā<lb break="no" n="13"/>ni prasādī-kr̥tāni kai<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->ści</supplied> <gap precision="low" quantity="5" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> yā rāja-bhogyatām āpāditāny a<lb break="no" n="14"/>smābhir bhavat-sāhāyyādi-karma-parituṣṭaiḥ śata-dvayan nuppunne bhagava<lb break="no" n="15"/>n-nārāyaṇasvāmino bhavadbhir eva kāraṇa-pūjādi-pravartanārtham pratipā
<lb n="16"/>ditan daśa-śatāni bhavatām eva pūrva-rāja-kr̥ta-vyavasthayā pratimucya
<lb n="17"/>daṅkhuṭṭārdhādi-karaṇīya-pratimocanārthaṁ liṅgvalśollādīnām aprave<lb break="no" n="18"/>śāya pūrva-rāja-śāsaneṣu ye prasādās teṣāṁ sarveṣām eva <supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->yuṣma</supplied><lb break="no" n="19"/>d-atisr̥ṣṭāṇām anumati-śāsanam idam asmābhir api prasādī-<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->kr̥ta</supplied><lb break="no" n="20"/>m evaṁ-vedibhir bhavadbhir asmat-prasāda-pratibaddha-jīvanair anyair vā <supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->na kaiści</supplied><lb break="no" n="21"/>d iyam ājñānyathā karaṇīyā yas tv etām ājñām utkra<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->myānyathā kari</supplied><lb break="no" n="22"/>ṣyate kārayiṣyate vā tasyotpatha<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->gāminaḥ</supplied> <gap precision="low" quantity="9" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>
<lb n="23"/><gap precision="low" quantity="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> ṇ vi <gap precision="low" quantity="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> ye <gap precision="low" quantity="15" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><!-- 
